        "TileImage": "$($repository 8c006449-1d24-478d-8248-e674897bc4da).Image",
        "Description": "I have now learned from this lab data that this woman in Mumbai, India is sickening random street people with spikes that contain this disease. &quot;This woman&quot; is called Neha. I don&apos;t know much about her, but what I do know is that she has hired at least two people to sicken people at the moment. I don&apos;t know much about them either, not even what they look like. Just their location. I would recommend the sniper rifle on this one. Good luck, hunting, and as always... Have fun!",
